description: Kline invited Kaleb to a big pool party he was supposedly having. When Kaleb got there, he realized HE WAS the party. Kline noticed how he had been looking at him and kept catching those glimpses of interest and attraction. He knew all he had to do was invite Kaleb over and have some one on one time. Kaleb was reluctant at first but then just went with what felt good. His first time will not soon be forgotten.
title: Anal Sensation
